{"tid":796074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得atm㩒機應該限時？","createTime":"2018-08-27T13:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T15:02:04.000Z","uid":203172,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e89d43a8fe93d37e5b9847d9288b986808b8ebf1","tid":796074,"uid":203172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲人見到條隊老撚咁長，都係到㩒㩒㩒唔知㩒乜鳩可以㩒成十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己企係到on99咁望住前面一張又一張通知書出黎，但唔知要等到何年何日先有得㩒個幾舊水個種無能為力真係慘過食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要過數又好點都好，見到條隊咁長咪排多次隊再過俾第二個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n尤其是啲呀嬸望住佢係咁係到撚部機，好似唔撚識用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係好想去助佢一臂之力，幫佢退翻張卡呀屌你老母！唔撚識用機就去銀行排隊入數啦屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計我話所有提款機應該係排隊到整個制 㩒一㩒部機就限時3分鐘，3分鐘後自動退卡，5分鐘內唔可以入翻同一張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3分鐘正常人類已經可以成功過完數或者㩒完錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以免啲冇公德心嘅人霸撚住部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贊成，最好㩒機要考牌，杜絕唔識㩒機嘅垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我大部時間，最鐘意等㩒機"},{"pid":"cc4d343b70bb703c04d4b630804913afd39223bf","tid":796074,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"應該<br />\n不過呢 樓豬如果你係醒嘅就唔需要煩排atm呢樣嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d8279cd23e38f6da3e54163f4cd8844df359e9","tid":796074,"uid":89509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得廢老出街都要考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f52e0332f6b9a2d4a8436ccf144d8ecee28a2d","tid":796074,"uid":87506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"你咪on9啦<br />\n佢地會死霸住部機<br />\n直到㩒到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99f995f6b06ebda71445bc54908256e96a6496a","tid":796074,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"中銀有阿 每次操作限時30秒"},{"pid":"7c64e08ca8f590d4cf19017a77bb2ced2bee6079","tid":796074,"uid":203172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4d343b70bb703c04d4b630804913afd39223bf","tid":796074,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"應該<br />\n不過呢 樓豬如果你係醒嘅就唔需要煩排atm呢樣嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"㩒錢唔喺atm 㩒可以係邊㩒？多人的話便利店/ 超市都多人啦 咪又係要排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5ffecfe13be1f79357b508b7e34ea44c0d0e45","tid":796074,"uid":203172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d8279cd23e38f6da3e54163f4cd8844df359e9","tid":796074,"uid":89509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得廢老出街都要考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"今日落雨 見識到擔遮都要考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb3a1851d89b20ff4ad9f683e5780c1011e6bb0","tid":796074,"uid":203172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5f52e0332f6b9a2d4a8436ccf144d8ecee28a2d","tid":796074,"uid":87506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl